dct_title_s: Commissioners official railway map of Missouri. Completed to January 1st 1888. Copyright 1887 by R.T. Higgins
dct_description_sm: Shows relief by hachures, drainage, names river valleys, indicates cities and towns, county boundaries, and the railroad network by distinguishing colors.
LC also has 1898 edition measuring 71 x 83 cm.; Description derived from published bibliography.
